<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8" ?>
<Defs>
	  <ScenarioDef>
		  <defName>Ark_Pathfinder</defName>
		  <label>寻路者</label>
		  <description>你们三位是出生在新拉特兰的萨科塔，从小在乐园长大使你们对外面的世界充满好奇，今天是每代萨科塔必然经历的远游的启程日，教宗并未给予你们任何使命，只是祝你们找到自己的道途，在同胞的欢呼声中你们走向了陌生的世界。</description>
		  <scenario>
			  <summary>三个萨科塔走出乐园，踏上未知的旅途。</summary>
			  <playerFaction>
				  <def>PlayerFaction</def>
				  <factionDef>PlayerColony</factionDef>
			  </playerFaction>
			  <parts>
				  <li Class="ScenPart_ConfigPage_ConfigureStartingPawns_Xenotypes">
					  <def>ConfigurePawnsXenotypes</def>
					  <pawnChoiceCount>8</pawnChoiceCount>
					  <xenotypeCounts>
						  <li>
							  <count>3</count>
							  <requiredAtStart>True</requiredAtStart>
							  <xenotype>Ark_SKT</xenotype>
							  <allowedDevelopmentalStages>Baby, Child, Adult</allowedDevelopmentalStages>
						  </li>
					  </xenotypeCounts>
				  </li>
				  <li Class="ScenPart_PlayerPawnsArriveMethod">
					  <def>PlayerPawnsArriveMethod</def>
				  </li>
				  <li Class="ScenPart_GameStartDialog">
					  <def>GameStartDialog</def>
					  <text>你们三位是出生在新拉特兰的萨科塔，从小在乐园长大使你们对外面的世界充满好奇，今天是每代萨科塔必然经历的远游的启程日，教宗并未给予你们任何使命，只是祝你们找到自己的道途，在同胞的欢呼声中你们走向了陌生的世界。</text>
					  <closeSound>GameStartSting</closeSound>
				  </li>
				  <li Class="ScenPart_StartingThing_Defined">
					  <def>StartingThing_Defined</def>
					  <thingDef>Silver</thingDef>
					  <count>2000</count>
				  </li>
				  <li Class="ScenPart_StartingThing_Defined">
					  <def>StartingThing_Defined</def>
					  <thingDef>MealSurvivalPack</thingDef>
					  <count>30</count>
				  </li>
				  <li Class="ScenPart_StartingThing_Defined">
					  <def>StartingThing_Defined</def>
					  <thingDef>MedicineIndustrial</thingDef>
					  <count>20</count>
				  </li>
				  <li Class="ScenPart_StartingThing_Defined">
					  <def>StartingThing_Defined</def>
					  <thingDef>ComponentIndustrial</thingDef>
					  <count>10</count>
				  </li>
				  <li Class="ScenPart_StartingThing_Defined">
					  <def>StartingThing_Defined</def>
					  <thingDef>WoodLog</thingDef>
					  <count>200</count>
				  </li>
				  <li Class="ScenPart_StartingThing_Defined">
					  <def>StartingThing_Defined</def>
					  <thingDef>Steel</thingDef>
					  <count>200</count>
				  </li>
				  <li Class="ScenPart_StartingResearch">
					  <def>StartingResearch</def>
					  <project>Machining</project>
				  </li>
				  <li Class="ScenPart_CreateIncident">
					  <def>CreateIncident</def>
					  <incident>GiveQuest_Random</incident>
					  <intervalDays>3</intervalDays>
					  <repeat>True</repeat>
				  </li>
				  <li Class="ScenPart_StartingThing_Defined">
					  <def>StartingThing_Defined</def>
					  <thingDef>Gun_BoltActionRifle</thingDef>
				  </li>
				  <li Class="ScenPart_StartingThing_Defined">
					  <def>StartingThing_Defined</def>
					  <thingDef>Gun_MachinePistol</thingDef>
				  </li>
				  <li Class="ScenPart_PawnFilter_Age">
					  <def>PawnFilter_Age</def>
					  <allowedAgeRange>17~21</allowedAgeRange>
				  </li>
			  </parts>
		  </scenario>
	  </ScenarioDef>
	  
	<ScenarioDef>
    <defName>Ark_SoloApostle</defName>
    <label>独行使徒</label>
    <description>你本以为这只是一次轻松的外派任务，但当爆炸声在运输机外响起，碎片与火花在你眼前伴随整个世界旋转时，你开始思念新拉特兰下水道里抓不完的偷渡者了。</description>
    <scenario>
      <summary>作为一名经验丰富的公证所执行者，在这个充满恶意的世界生存下去。</summary>
      <playerFaction>
        <def>PlayerFaction</def>
        <factionDef>PlayerColony</factionDef>
      </playerFaction>
      <parts>
		  <li Class="ScenPart_ConfigPage_ConfigureStartingPawns_Xenotypes">
			  <def>ConfigurePawnsXenotypes</def>
			  <pawnChoiceCount>8</pawnChoiceCount>
			  <xenotypeCounts>
				  <li>
					  <requiredAtStart>True</requiredAtStart>
					  <xenotype>Ark_SKT</xenotype>
					  <allowedDevelopmentalStages>Baby, Child, Adult</allowedDevelopmentalStages>
				  </li>
			  </xenotypeCounts>
		  </li>
		  <li Class="ScenPart_PlayerPawnsArriveMethod">
			  <def>PlayerPawnsArriveMethod</def>
			  <method>DropPods</method>
		  </li>
		  <li Class="ScenPart_GameStartDialog">
			  <def>GameStartDialog</def>
			  <text>你本以为这只是一次轻松的外派任务，但当爆炸声在运输机外响起，碎片与火花在你眼前伴随整个世界旋转时，你开始思念新拉特兰下水道里抓不完的偷渡者了。</text>
			  <closeSound>GameStartSting</closeSound>
		  </li>
		  <li Class="ScenPart_StartingThing_Defined">
			  <def>StartingThing_Defined</def>
			  <thingDef>MealSurvivalPack</thingDef>
			  <count>30</count>
		  </li>
		  <li Class="ScenPart_StartingThing_Defined">
			  <def>StartingThing_Defined</def>
			  <thingDef>MedicineIndustrial</thingDef>
			  <count>20</count>
		  </li>
		  <li Class="ScenPart_StartingResearch">
			  <def>StartingResearch</def>
			  <project>Machining</project>
		  </li>
		  <li Class="ScenPart_CreateIncident">
			  <def>CreateIncident</def>
			  <incident>ShipChunkDrop</incident>
			  <intervalDays>1</intervalDays>
		  </li>
		  <li Class="ScenPart_StartingThing_Defined">
			  <def>StartingThing_Defined</def>
			  <thingDef>Ark_AssaultRifle</thingDef>
		  </li>
		  <li Class="ScenPart_CreateIncident">
			  <def>CreateIncident</def>
			  <incident>RaidEnemy</incident>
			  <intervalDays>6</intervalDays>
			  <repeat>True</repeat>
		  </li>
		  <li Class="ScenPart_StartingThing_Defined">
			  <def>StartingThing_Defined</def>
			  <thingDef>Apparel_FlakJacket</thingDef>
			  <quality>Excellent</quality>
		  </li>
		  <li Class="ScenPart_StartingThing_Defined">
			  <def>StartingThing_Defined</def>
			  <thingDef>Apparel_FlakVest</thingDef>
			  <quality>Excellent</quality>
		  </li>
		  <li Class="ScenPart_StartingThing_Defined">
			  <def>StartingThing_Defined</def>
			  <thingDef>Apparel_FlakPants</thingDef>
			  <quality>Excellent</quality>
		  </li>
		  <li Class="ScenPart_ScatterThingsNearPlayerStart">
			  <def>ScatterThingsNearPlayerStart</def>
			  <thingDef>ShuttleCrashed</thingDef>
			  <allowRoofed>True</allowRoofed>
		  </li>
      </parts>
    </scenario>
  </ScenarioDef>

</Defs>